### Data Flow Summary

```
Every N seconds:
  1. TradingBot._scan_all()
  2. Load news events  в”Җв”Җв–ә filter blackout window
  3. RiskManager.can_trade() в”Җв”Җв–ә check drawdown limits
  4. For each symbol:
       a. MT5Connector.get_ohlcv(H4, H1, M15)
       b. SignalEngine.evaluate() в”Җв”Җв–ә Three Strikes analysis
       c. SignalLogger.log()      в”Җв”Җв–ә append to CSV
       d. If EXECUTE TRADE:
            ExecutionClient.place_order()
            в””в”Җв”Җ POST http://windows-ec2:8000/buy (or /sell)
                в””в”Җв”Җ mt5.order_send() on Windows
```

